item.title: Sixt
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
SIXT Ljubljana DT office is located at the central Bus & Railway station in Ljubljana in direct vicinity of the old city center. Office can be found at the western entrance to the Bus station, betweenbus lanes 4 & 5. Ljubljana is a great starting point to visit Slovene's beautiful cultural and natural landmarks as it is located practically in the heart of our country. Everything is practically within one hour reach - either you decide to take the trip to the oldest town in Ptuj, maybe visit natural springs of Rogaska Slatina, or go exploring the caves in Postojna or Skocjan.
In the winter you can go to Kranjska gora or Krvavec to check the ski slopes or in the summer cool down in the Sea and visit Piran and Portoroz along the way- or if this is not refreshing enough for you- go to the region of Gorenjska, make some hiking tours and when returning take a swim in the beautiful lake Bohinj or Bled. Ask our agents for any recommendation on where to go to - we're here for you! Ljubljana offers a lot of sightseeing tours as well - and you can reach them all on foot if you start from our branch - if you got on Miklosiceva street in 10 minutes you arrive to the Presern square with the beautiful Tromostovje - the three bridges accros Ljubljanica river, designed by our famous architect Joze Plecnik. You can follow the banks of the river and feel the heartbeat of Ljubljana in a number of cafes and restaurants nearby. You can also go to Ljubljanski grad - on foot or with a funicular railway.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: The sight is everything I wanted it to be! It is just a gorgeous piece of history and architecture. Go over it, go under it, drive across it, and bike around it; it will not disappoint.

For strange high level views over London this is a great place. If you are a person interested in how the bridge moves aside for shipping this is a must. The inside offers viewing of the previous hydraulic mechanisms, a tribute to Victorian and early 20th century engineering.

item.title: Ljubljana Castle
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The Ljubljana Castle has been owned by the city since 1905, when the then mayor Ivan Hribar purchased it from state authorities. In late December of 2010, at the beginning of the Mayor Zoran Janković’s second term, the City Municipality of Ljubljana established the independent public institute Ljubljana Castle. The institute organizes and conducts cultural, artistic, touristic and other events with the purpose of developing a comprehensive cultural and tourist offer. Here, the treasures of cultural heritage preservation intertwine with eclectic contemporary art by Slovenian and foreign artists. Within the framework of youth programmes, the institute conducts pedagogic and adult education projects related to the castle and its surroundings. The Ljubljana Castle institute preserves and promotes the castle's material and intangible heritage. The permanent museum exhibitions at the Ljubljana Castle are the Virtual Castle, Slovenian History, the Museum of Puppetry, Penitentiary and iLjubljana. The institute plans, designs and markets a comprehensive tourist offer in the area of the Ljubljana Castle and the Castle Hill. Through the tourist information centre, the institute informs visitors on all events taking place in the area. The Ljubljana Castle operates a tramway ascending the hill into the castle, in this manner connecting the city core with the Castle Hill. The institute’s programme brings together various public cultural institutions, tourist associations and other operators of cultural and tourist events in the public interest.

item.title: Narodni muzej Slovenije
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Dear Visitors, The National Museum of Slovenia, which was founded by the Carniolan State Parliament on the 15th of October 1821, is the oldest of all Slovenian museum institutions. Its six departments collect, document, preserve, and investigate the mobile cultural heritage of Slovenia and present it to the public. Thanks to the exceptional educational level of its staff members, the museum also has the status of a research institution, and is involved in several scientific research projects focused on a more detailed study of the Slovenian cultural heritage. The quality of the museum activities in the central national museum depends on the staff and its consultants, with their excellent professional command of their fields and specific areas of specialization. Only through such an approach is it possible to present the cultural heritage of Slovenia to the public in a modern, attractive, and popular manner. The museum wishes to illuminate in detail through the presentation of material (in the form of scientific and popular publications and exhibitions) individual segments of the history of present-day Slovenia and make this available to the widest possible public. With the digitalization of material and the construction of an electronic database about the cultural heritage that its preserves, the National Museum of Slovenia has joined similar European institutions that are attempting to enable the broadest possible access to items of the cultural heritage through the use of modern information technology. Dear visitors to the National Museum of Slovenia, you are invited to attend lectures, to take guided tours with experts, to view the finest objects of the Slovenian heritage that speak of the history of this land throughout all periods, to bring your children to workshops, and to choose for your friends and acquaintances gifts of replicas of some of our monuments, which you can purchase in our museum shop. Welcome to the National Museum of Slovenia!

item.title: BKS Banka
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Die BKS Bank mit Sitz in Klagenfurt, Österreich, beschäftigt über 1.100 Mitarbeiter. Wir bieten alle Bank- und Finanzdienstleistungen für Privat- und Firmenkunden. Die BKS Bank hat Filialen in Österreich, Slowenien, Kroatien und der Slowakei. In Ungarn und Italien verfügt unser Haus über Repräsentanzen. Unsere Geschäftspolitik ist nachhaltig ausgerichtet und setzt auf langfristigen Erfolg statt kurzfristigen Gewinn. Wir sind ein verlässlicher Bankpartner für unsere Kunden, bieten unseren Mitarbeitern sichere Arbeitsplätze und engagieren uns für unsere Gesellschaft und die Umwelt.
Servicezeiten: Unser Social Media-Team ist für Sie Montag bis Donnerstag von 8.00 bis 16.00 Uhr und Freitags von 8.00 bis 15.00 Uhr da.

item.title: Opera
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Morda se res zdi, da imajo institucionalno gledališče pa glasbeno gledališče in balet na Slovenskem v primerjavi z drugimi evropskimi okolji kratko dobo, vendar lahko glede na vse zgodovinske okoliščine brez večjih zadržkov s ponosom pogledamo v preteklost. Zgodovina našega odra je bila živahna, še posebej zato, ker je preteklo precej let, preden smo lahko rekli, da je na njem zavladala domena slovenskih umetnikov in ustvarjalcev ter da so ti v večini postali člani naših stalnih ansamblov. Od tistega trenutka dalje, ko je na pot profesionalizacije stopil ljubljanski baletni ansambel in mu je sledil še orkester našega gledališča, pa vse do danes, je minilo že več kot 90 let. Preletimo na kratko nekaj desetletij: ko je leta 1892 slovensko Deželno gledališče dobilo novo poslopje (današnjo Opero), so se v njem uprizarjale dramske in operne predstave, hkrati pa tudi nemške. V njegovem okviru je dobila Opera stalno angažirane dirigente, soliste in zbor, predstave pa so spremljali sprva najeti vojaški glasbeniki, od leta 1908 pa člani novoustanovljene Slovenske filharmonije. Leta 1911 se je nemško gledališče preselilo v novo stavbo (današnjo Dramo). V času prve svetovne vojne so muze v ljubljanski Operi molčale, v gledališki stavbi je domoval kinematograf Central, dokler ni spomladi leta 1918 ponovnemu zagonu gledališča botroval Gledališki konzorcij, ki si je zastavil cilj, da bi v sezoni 1918/19 začelo ponovno delovati slovenski oder. In tako je slovensko glasbeno prizorišče ponovno oživelo že isto jesen, domači gledališki prostor pa je poleg dramskega in opernega dobil še baletno gledališče. Na ljubljanskem odru so takrat izvajali predvsem francoske in italijanske opere, poudarek pa je bil tudi na slovanskih in slovenskih opernih delih. V obdobju med obema vojnama je operno gledališče posodobilo svoj repertoar in uprizoritev je doživelo kar nekaj uspešnih oper slovenskih avtorjev (Kogoj, Osterc, Bravničar). Po drugi svetovni vojni je postal ljubljanski ansambel cenjen tudi zunaj meja domovine. Velikanski uspeh je požel z mednarodnim gostovanjem na Nizozemskem, še zlasti pa z uspešnim nastopom v velikem opernem gledališču v Parizu. Leta 1957 je bil posnetek opere Zaljubljen v tri oranže S. Prokofjeva (dirigent Bogo Leskovic) nagrajen s Philipsovo nagrado grand prix kot najboljši posnetek leta. S prvimi predstavami v okviru opernih in operetnih premier v jesenskem delu sezone 1918/1919, spomladi 1919 pa s svojo prvo samostojno baletno premiero Ugrabljena Evelina, je začel svojo poklicno pot tudi naš balet z lastnim ansamblom in vodjem. Že v prvih letih svojega obstoja je uprizoril nekaj znanih klasičnih baletnih stvaritev, svoj repertoar pa je obogatil tudi z novejšimi slovenskimi deli. Doslej si je ljubljansko občinstvo lahko ogledalo veliko število različnih baletnih predstav iz klasičnega repertoarja, med njimi pa tudi precej novejših stvaritev slovenskih in tujih koreografov. Danes se osrednje slovensko glasbeno gledališče – poleg rednih programskih novosti vsake sezone – ponaša z obširnim repertoarjem opernih, baletnih in koncertnih del iz sodobne in klasične glasbeno-gledališke ustvarjalnosti v matični hiši ter na gostovanjih doma in v tujini. Slovensko narodno gledališče Opera in balet Ljubljana že nekaj let uspešno sodeluje tudi z različnimi mednarodnimi in domačimi koproducenti, s katerimi je v minulih sezonah uprizorilo več odmevnih projektov (Faust, Aida, Zaljubljen v tri oranže, Don Kihot, Knez Igor, Rusalka, …), prav gotovo pa je bila med najodmevnejšimi svetovna premiera ponovno odkrite Offenbachove opere Renske nimfe.

item.title: Plato
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Just a minute's walk from Trafalgar Square, the flagship BB Bakery is an impressive hideaway. A team of French pastry chefs adhere to your every whim, providing classic French delicacies, freshly squeezed orange juice and even a selection of fine tea from Betjeman & Barton, served in a proper tea pot.
Whether you want to meet friends for a coffee and a pastry, relax in our comfy chairs over a spot of lunch or experience our fabulous afternoon tea, we look forward to sharing our passion for food and baking with you. You can also enjoy our unique and hugely popular BB Afternoon Tea Tour on a Routemaster Bus, whilst taking in the sights of London. We also offer gluten free, vegetarian and Halal Afternoon Teas.

item.title: Slovenska Hisa
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Slovenska hiša je prostor kjer vaše brbončice osvežijo spomin na pristno domačo slovensko hrano in pijačo. Za vas smo izbrali jedi, ki veljajo za slovensko posebnost, so geografsko zaščitene ali so v ponudbi preprosto zato, ker so nam všeč.
Želimo, da se pri nas sprostite in uživate v okusih tradicije. Morda česa slovenskega še ne poznate, a se bo to kmalu spremenilo. Jejte, pijte in se veselite. Naj bo Slovenska hiša vaše stičišče s podeželjem in urbanim mestnim utripom.

item.title: Central Station
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Every decent city is known by it’s own preparty landmark. The one in Ljubljana is called Centralna postaja (Central Station) and it’s a place where you can stop for a coffee, quick in person or online chat, catch up with your friends or drop for simple, affordable and tasty bite during the lunch break. This is a spot where you can enjoy urban music, find information about what’s hot on the scene and what’s going on in Ljubljana and Slovenia, buy tickets for events or party with us into the night once the place transforms into music, drink, snack & party space in the evening. RADIO STATION, INFOPOINT, DRINK, COCKTAIL, STREET FOOD, COMFORTABLE SMOKINGA AREA & PARTY. Don’t Hesitate! START HERE.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: I was in London last week and my friend who lives there told me to meet her at Pizza East for Sunday brunch! I said, "Pizza?!" I really want brunch! She said, "Trust me on this one!" I'm so glad that I did! Amazing avocado-toast with eggs. But I'm so glad I had the pizza too! With all due respects to Nancy Silverton at Mozza in Los Angeles, this pizza trumps hers! (and I love hers!!) This is better. "Trust me on this one!"

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: This is a family run Pizzeria and restaurant. The service is always friendly and warm. The menu is extensive and they will cook to order where they can. The Risotto's are delicious, we take away and eat in.

You need to lift your game for regulars to continue dining here. First impressions count. The service is a huge let down along with just now ordinary food. Such a shame as this was one of our favourite local restaurants.

item.title: Id
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Mi smo doma v Ljubljani, v steklenem mezaninu, Ravnikarjevem primerku slovenske moderne, postavljenem na stičišče Gregorčičeve in Slovenske ceste v Ljubljani. Ta skrbno zasnovan volumen prostora že vrsto let podobno skrbno polnimo z izbrano notranjo opremo velikih oblikovalskih imen, modernih in sodobnih klasik.
Smo arhitekturni biro in prodajni salon notranje opreme urejen po podobi doma. Kuhinja, dnevna soba in spalni del so v polni uporabi vsak delovni dan. Naš dom v izložbi je zaradi svoje igre z večnamembnostjo prostora zavzel močno identiteto. Postal je id:doma, bivanjsko doživetje za nas, redne stranke in mimoidoče.
Vzemite si čas za obisk, celostno izkušnjo v živo, pa za klepet z nami, strokovnjaki.
Z veseljem se vam posvetimo vsak delovnik med 10. in 19. uro ali po dogovoru.

item.title: Falafel
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: V osrčju Ljubljane je prijetna, v orientalskem slogu opremljena okrepčevalnica Abi Falafel. Prvi lokal s tipično arabsko hrano v Slovenji vodi družina Shaar. Znani smo po veliki ljubezni do kuhanja, saj so naše jedi osvojile marsikatero gurmansko srce. K nam zahajajo ljudje, ki ljubijo pestrost, nove vonje in okuse tujih dežel, in se želijo zdravo prehranjevati. Hrano vam pripravljamo sproti. Trudimo se, da ste postreženi hitro in prijazno. O tem se lahko prepričate, ko nas obiščete. Strežemo mesne in vegetarijanske jedi, z veliko sveže, predvsem presne zelenjave. Posladkate se lahko s slovitimi orientalskimi slaščicami in vse poplaknete z kardamomovim čajem. Naj bo to zajtrk, prigrizek med delom, kosilo, večerja ali pa pogostitev prijateljev, v Falaflu zadovoljimo vsak okus.

item.title: Odeja
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Podjetje Odeja d.o.o. je vodilni slovenski proizvajalec vrhunskih prešitih tekstilnih izdelkov. Naš bogat proizvodni program obsega izdelke za opremo postelje in polepšanje doma. Z našo ponudbo lahko opremite spalnico in otroško posteljico, uredite kopalnico, popestrite kuhinjo in dnevno sobo ali pa opremite ležišča in prostore gostinskih, hotelskih ter zdravstvenih objektov. Lasten razvoj in proizvodnja, nadzorovana izbira najboljših materialov in vrhunska izdelava so glavne značilnosti podjetja Odeja. Omogočajo nam, da se lahko vsakemu kupcu prilagodimo glede materialov, načina izdelave in količine izdelkov. Poslovnim partnerjem pomagamo uresničiti idejo in razviti zelo specifične izdelke za nišni ali široki trg. Večino našega trga predstavljajo zahtevni kupci, ki prisegajo na preverjen izvor materialov, vrhunsko izdelavo ter optimalno razmerje med kvaliteto in ceno izdelkov. Imamo lastno mrežo maloprodajnih trgovin v vseh večjih slovenskih krajih in spletno trgovino za globalni trg. Poslovne partnerje in naročnike imamo v številnih državah sveta, zaradi preverjene kvalitete in izvora izdelkov pa svoj trg vsako leto širimo.

item.title: Traditional Slovenian Evening
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Introduce yourself (Folklore group, you personally, how long does this group exist, how long are you part of it.) Hello, my name is Nika and I have been a part of our group for almost 4 years now. But the group exist much longer than that, it was established in 1948 by renown Slovenian musician, choir conductor and ethnologist, France Marolt. The group is actually named after him and is a shining sign of folklore activity in Slovenia. I joined the group as a first-year-student who just moved to Ljubljana for her studies. At first I was still deciding whether to join the choir or folklore group, but then a dear friend of mine persuaded me to join the dancing group. And I must say, there was not a day in my life that I would regret this decision! The group’s main active members are students from all over Slovenia, that come to study to Ljubljana and this diversity is something that makes our life in organization even more fun and interesting. We have performances all over the country and every year we prepare the annual concert which is held in Slovenia’s most renown cultural hall, the Cankarjev dom in Ljubljana. Students combining passion for dance, love for cultural heritage, interest for cultural diversity of our ethnic area and most of all the joy of being in a young and happy group as this – this is who we are!

item.content:encoded:
Along with office buildings and residential apartments, Paddington Central is also home to a gym, a number of quick lunch stops cafes as well as several canal side bars and restaurants.

Local Running Routes

Enjoy a lunchtime run along Regent’s Canal, an almost traffic-free jog through the heart and soul of London.

Little Venice

A tranquil area affectionately known as Little Venice lies to the north of Paddington Central, waiting to be explored.

The Quince Tree

Nestled inside the award-winning Clifton Nurseries, the Quince Tree Café offers fabulous brunches, lunches, finest coffees and afternoon teas. Daily specials prove popular with its Little Venice and Paddington neighbours.

Bombay Palace

Just five minutes from Praed Street in Connaught Village, Bombay Palace is one of London's best authentic Indian restaurants.

item.title: Dinner in the Sky
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Dinner in the Sky®, nepozabno kulinarično doživetje visoko med oblaki je s edinstvenim konceptom obnorelo svet. Nepozaben ambient, prečudovit razgled na mesto in kulinarične stvaritve najboljših kuharjev – vse to obeta nepozaben dogodek Dinner in the Sky®.

Dogodek bo potekal v središču Ljubljane, kjer vas bo kar 50 metrov nad tlemi pričakala miza, ki hkrati sprejme 22 gostov. Udeležite se tega nepozabnega dogodka z družino ali prijatelji in se prepustite kulinaričnemu razvajanju! Vrhunski kuharski mojstri vam bodo visoko nad oblaki postregli s prefinjenimi kulinaričnimi dobrotami, ki vam bodo še dolgo ostale v spominu. Na dogodkih Dinner in the Sky® vam bodo postregli vrhunski kuharski mojstri. Če se boste udeležili večernega dogodka, se vam bo kuharski mojster pridružil kar med oblaki in vam 50 metrov nad tlemi postregel z jedmi. Edinstven ambient, izjemna kulinarika in priložnost, da se iz oči v oči srečate z vrhunskimi kuharskimi mojstri, se vam bodo za vedno vtisnili v spomin. Ljubljano boste tako doživeli na prav poseben način.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Bruce Poole and Nigel Platts-Martin opened Chez Bruce in 1995. From the outset, it was their intention to serve the very best food and drink but within a relaxed, informal yet thoroughly professionally orchestrated environment. At Chez Bruce we are not particularly into gadgets and tricks in the kitchen. Home-made charcuterie, slow cooked braises, offal, warm and cold salads, classical desserts and bread-making could be listed as specialities. We also take the cheese board very seriously indeed and it forms an integral part of the restaurant's day-to-day life. The Directors of the restaurant are fanatical wine-lovers and are very proud of the restaurant's wine list which truly is one of the very best in the UK.
business meetings, dining, romantic, special occasion
French cooking with hints of the Mediterranean

item.title: Park Špica
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Le deset minut od centra Ljubljane se nahaja prenovljeno nabrežje Ljubljanice, ki je znano po imenu Špica (ime izhaja iz špičastega kopnega dela). Špica je bila nekoč ljubljansko kopališče in tudi danes je zaradi prijetnih zelenih in lesenih površin Špica videti kot plaža, kjer številni Ljubljančani in obiskovalci Ljubljane v lepih dnevih lovijo sončne žarke. Leta 2009 je bil odprt tudi nov most, 38 metrov dolga Hladnikova brv na Špici, ki mesto povezuje z zelenim zaledjem, predmestjem in Botaničnim vrtom. Brv je zamišljena kot ultralahka struktura, namenjena pa je pešcem in kolesarjem.

item.title: Best Western Premier Hotel Slon
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Set in the heart of Ljubljana, the Best Western Premier Hotel Slon offers bright and colourful rooms, a spa area, an elegant restaurant and a well-known pastry shop. An extensive buffet breakfast with Italian Espresso Coffee is served in the stylish breakfast room. The 4-star superior rooms feature lavishly decorated interiors and luxurious bed linen. Each room is air conditioned and fitted with modern amenities. The hotel's Spa & Fitness features a state-of-the-art fitness centre open 24/7, equipped with Technogym machines providing all the latest cardiovascular and weight training facilities, as well as relaxing saunas with tropical rain showers. A choice of 9 different Thai massage treatments at the hotel's Thai Massage & Spa offers a chance to unwind and relax. The stylishly appointed Slon 1552 Restaurant with large windows overlooking the busy pedestrian part of the old town is a popular meeting place for both locals and hotel guests. It serves Slovene, Mediterranean and international cuisine accompanied by fine wines. Seasonal menus feature unusual and locally grown ingredients fresh from the marketplace. Daily menus featuring special 3-course lunches are offered as well, including vegetarian and vegan dishes. Wines and cocktails are served into the late hours. Hotel Slon Convention Centre comprises 5 multifunctional conference rooms, all well-lit by natural daylight and air conditioned. They are also partitionable and therefore suitable for various meetings and events. In just a few steps you can reach the famous Three Bridges and other centrally located tourist attractions, business locations and major government offices in Ljubljana.

This is our guests' favourite part of Ljubljana, according to independent reviews.

This property also has one of the best-rated locations in Ljubljana! Guests are happier about it compared to other properties in the area.

We speak your language!

item.title: Park Tivoli
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Tivoli Park is Ljubljana's largest and most beautiful park, stretching right into the city centre. It was designed in 1813 by the French engineer Jean Blanchard and created by joining together the parks which had surrounded Podturn and Cekin Mansions. The park, covering an area of approximately five square kilometres, is crossed by three grand horse chestnut tree-lined walks and landscaped with ornamental flower beds, interesting trees and numerous statues and fountains. The park area blends into the slopes of the Rožnik hill, to which it is connected by several walking paths and a trim trail with several exercise stations along its length. Jakopič Promenade, a popular outdoor gallery Tivoli Park's scenic Jakopič Promenade (Jakopičevo sprehajališče), designed by the architect Jože Plečnik in the central part of Tivoli Park, has become a well known outdoor venue for exhibitions of large-format photographs, open throughout the year.

Location details

Since its general layout was made in 1813, Tivoli Park has seen several expansions and re-landscaping projects, including the building of a fish pond on its western edge in 1880. Next to the pond there is a small botanical garden with a glasshouse, whose management was entrusted to the Ljubljana Botanic Garden on its 200th anniversary in 2010. The glasshouse houses a permanent exhibition of tropical and carnivorous plants. Across the way from the fish pond, a children's playground was built in 1942 and refurbished with new play equipment in 1994. Between 1921 and 1939, an extensive re-design project was undertaken by the architect Jože Plečnik, who designed the park's wide Jakopič Promenade, which ends at the bottom of the stairway leading to Tivoli Mansion. The promenade is named after the Slovenian Impressionist painter Rihard Jakopič. In 1929, the Letno Kopališče Ilirija outdoor swimming pool was built at the edge of the Tivoli park to a design by Stanko Bloudek. At the time when it was built it was the most modern swimming pool in the Kingdom of Yugoslavia. In memory of Bloudek, a sports park bearing his name was later built in front of the Tivoli park's Cekin Mansion (Cekinov grad). It included tennis and basketball courts, a roller-skating rink and a children's playground designed by the architect Marjan Božič. In 1965, Božič also designed Dvorana Tivoli, a hall intended for sports events and larger concerts. Not far away, a sports and recreational centre with an indoor swimming pool, fitness facilities and a bowling alley was built to a design by Fedja Košir in 1973.

item.title: Pivnica Union
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Pivnica Pivovarne Union je stičišče dobrega piva in kulinarike. V njej trčita sodobni svet in tradicija, ki sta združena v celovito zgodbo. V ponudbi je kar 10 različnih točenih piv. Celoten asortiman piv Pivovarne Union ter del asortimana pivovarne Laško. Posebej za pivnico pa naši tehnologi vsak mesec pripravijo posebno pivo imenovano Pivovarjev izbor. Kulinarika v pivnici predstavlja Slovenijo, slovensko kuhinjo, vendar s sodobnim pridihom. Vključuje menije, ki so vezani na posamezno vrsto ponujenega piva, vključuje jedi, ki obujajo slovensko in ljubljansko kulinarično tradicijo ter sezonske jedi. Prijetno vzdušje pivnice pa zaokrožamo s programom, ki se iz meseca v mesec spreminja.

item.title: Vander Urbani Resort
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Featuring a rooftop swimming pool, Vander Urbani Resort design hotel enjoys a quiet location in the very heart of Ljubljana's centre. Its guests can enjoy an on-site restaurant and modern-style accommodation, only 200 m from the Main Square. Free Wi-Fi is provided. All carefully designed rooms come with modern furnishings and feature a seating area and a fully equipped bathroom. Amenities in each unit include a flat-screen satellite TV, a minibar and air conditioning. The Vander Urbani Resort’s restaurant serves local cuisine and gourmet snacks. Guests can enjoy an extensive selection of wines from the wine cellar. A common terrace is equipped with sun loungers. Massage and beauty treatments are also available. Guests can explore Ljubljana’s vibrant centre filled with restaurants, bars and cafes. Ljubljana Castle is a 10-minute walk away. Car and bike rental can be organised upon request. The Main Bus and Train Station can be reached within 500 m. Ljubljana Airport is at the distance of 27 km.

This is our guests' favourite part of Ljubljana, according to independent reviews.

This property also has one of the best-rated locations in Ljubljana! Guests are happier about it compared to other properties in the area.

We speak your language!

item.title: Tehniški muzej Slovenije
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Tehniški muzej Slovenije se nahaja v nekdanjem kartuzijanskem samostanu v Bistri pri Vrhniki, ki je od Ljubljane oddaljen le dvajset kilometrov. Obiskovalci si lahko poleg ogleda muzejskih zbirk privoščijo prijeten počitek v mirnem naravnem okolju, stran od mestnega vrveža, ob pomirjajočih zvokih žuborečega muzejskega potoka. Med samostanskimi zidovi in hodniki so na ogled številne stalne zbirke s področja kmetijstva, prometa, gozdarstva, lesarstva, lovstva, ribištva, tekstila, elektrotehnike in tiskarstva. Veliko pozornosti obiskovalci namenijo zbirki Titovih avtomobilov in napravam na vodni pogon, kot so žitni mlin, orodna kovačija, rekonstruiran pogonski obrat furnirnice ter žaga venecijanka. Delovanje nekaterih je v okviru nedeljskih demonstracij tudi na ogled. Predmeti in naprave, ki jih odkrivamo v zbirkah, v sebi nosijo mnoge zabavne, poučne in zanimive zgodbe ter odgovarjajo na marsikatera vprašanja: Kakšen avto so vozili moji stari starši? Kako je kruh pekla moja babica? S čim so tkali obleke? Poleg vodstev po razstavah v slovenskem, angleškem, italijanskem in nemškem jeziku, muzej ponuja tudi številne tečaje, delavnice ter vsako nedeljo tudi demonstracije, preko katerih lahko mladi in odrasli obiskovalci resnično začutijo tehnološki duh preteklosti. Po predhodnem dogovoru je možna organizacija delavnic in demonstracij izven objavljenih urnikov. V muzeju potekajo tudi festivali, ki jih pripravljamo v sodelovanju z drugimi izobraževalnimi institucijami.

item.title: Akron
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Akron že več kot 26 let nudi celovite rešitve opremljanja z vgradnimi omarami in drugim pohištvom ter dosega zavidljive rezultate.  Prepoznate ga po vgradnih omarah z drsnimi vrati, predelnih stenah, spalnicah, otroških sobah in ostalem pohištvu po meri. Opremlja vse vrste prostorov, od spalnic in garderobnih sob do otroških in dnevnih sob, kopalnic, mansard, predsob, pisarn ipd. S stalnim razvojem in prepoznavanjem poslovnih priložnosti Akron presega okvire pričakovanj, ter z upoštevanjem tržnih trendov ustvarja izjemno dodano vrednost. Uspeh seveda ni naključje. Vse aktivnosti so usmerjene h kupcem, k prepoznavanju in zadovoljevanju njihovih pričakovanj. Sodelavci Akrona svoje delo opravljajo predano in vrhunsko, kar se odraža v zadovoljstvu kupcev, ki se z veseljem vračajo. Blagovna znamka Akron je prepoznavna v domačem okolju, vedno bolj pa utira in pušča sledi tudi izven meja. Prodajni program pohištva Akron najdete v več kot 20 salonih po Sloveniji (link), kakor tudi v tujini. Najbolj opremljen je specializirani razstavni salon v Ljubljani, ki nudi široko paleto vzorcev. Le-te je mogoče na najrazličnejše načine uporabiti tako pri vgradnih omarah kot pri ostalem prodajnem programu. Vrhunsko usposobljeni svetovalci vam z veseljem predstavijo celoten prodajni program, možne rešitve vaših prostorskih težav ter se z vami dogovorijo za izmero in ogled prostora pri vas doma. Tehnološko podprta proizvodnja in lasten razvoj omogočata natančno in kvalitetno izdelavo pohištva. Optimizacija proizvodnje nudi možnost, da kupcu že ob naročilu vgradne omare  sporočimo točen datum montaže. Vgradni elementi se nekaj dni pred montažo dostavijo na dom, kjer usposobljena ekipa monterjev poskrbi za kvalitetno in natančno vgradnjo. Po preteku 5-letne garancije je servis zagotovljen še  nadaljnjih 10 let. Prednosti vodilnega proizvajalca vgradnih omar je veliko, vse pa vodijo k ustvarjanju dobrih zgodb sodobnega opremljanja. Z jasno vizijo razvoja novih produktov in kvalitetno storitvijo0 bo Akron upravičeval pričakovanja tudi v prihodnje

item.title: Delight Ljubljana
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Delight Office Solution je podjetje, specializirano za opremljanje, dizajniranje in projektiranje poslovnih interierjev, kot tudi za izvajanje zaključnih del v gradbeništvu. S svojimi pisarnami v Sloveniji, Hrvaški, Črni Gori, Srbiji in Makedoniji želimo zagotoviti enako kvaliteto storitev in podpore v celotni regiji.
Podjetje je ustanovljeno pred več kot 10 leti, in od takrat kontinuirano nadgrajuje potrfolio svojih proizvodov in storitev. Svojim strankam želi nuditi kreativno, praktično in ekonomično rešitev. Celovita rešitev za pisarniški prostor je sinonim podjetja Delight.
Vsi ti elementi potrjujejo našo odločnost v prizadevanju da postanemo vodilno podjetje, katero nudi predvsem znanje in izkušnje v opremljanju poslovnih interierjev, s ciljem kreiranja delovnega prostora prihodnosti.

item.title: Luda
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Začela sva jeseni 2011 v Hiši Denk in si nekaj mesecev širila obzorja, spomladi 2012 pa organizirala prvo pop up restavracijo Dada. Konec leta je ob Pop-up Domu spontano nastal kolektiv Trapez, s katerim smo v 2013 izpeljali več kot 30 dogodkov, povezanih s hrano. Še vedno sva rada del Trapeza.
Kuhala bova jedi, ki bi jih tudi sama želela dobiti na mizo. Zavedava se, da morava veliko izkušenj še dobiti, a verjameva, da bo Luda zato vedno boljša.
Vesela bova, če boš užival-a, v tem je bistvo vsega. Urška & Luka, oktober 2014

item.title: Nova ljubljanska banka
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
NLB je danes drugačna banka
Banka s poslanstvom je veliko več kot seštevek dejavnosti. Svoj vpliv na finančnem trgu NLB utrjuje z aktivno vlogo na področjih družbenega razvoja. Aktivni smo v komunikaciji s strankami. Izpolnjujemo svoje obljube ter jasno povemo, kaj lahko in česa ne moremo narediti. Smo odzivni in dostopni. Vračamo se v tradicionalno bančništvo, na strateške trge in segmente. Aktivno dezinvestiramo nestrateške dejavnosti. Celovito pristopamo k upravljanju s tveganji, ki temelji na strokovnih kriterijih in smiselno konzervativnem ter premišljenem dojemanju vseh vrst tveganj. Prevzemamo zmerna tveganja. Racionaliziramo procese s ciljem vzpostaviti vitko organizacijo. Poudarjamo integriteto ter proaktivno komunikacijo le-te in drugih pozitivnih vrednot. Zavezani smo k delovanju skladno z zakonodajo, s pravili stroke, z načeli odličnosti in integritete.

item.title: Kolosej
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
In the last decade the cinema exhibition industry in Slovenia has gone through a complete metamorphosis and Kolosej has played a key role with an active approach to their development. Since 2001, when the first Kolosej opened, several other multiplexes opened in Slovenia, covering most regions in the country. Businesses that have traditionally dealt with cinema exhibition and the activities directly connected to it, like bars and restaurants, have now widened the range of their services and have become true entertainment centers.
Nonetheless, cinema exhibition is still one of the basic activities of Kolosej, since the sale of tickets represents a substantial part of its income. In 2001 Kolosej had a 55% market share (the number of visitors to the cinemas) and in the years 2005 and 2006 this share has leveled off at approximately 72%.

item.title: Argentino
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prisrčno pozdravljeni in dobrodošli v steakhousu ARGENTINO! Prepustite se kulinaričnemu razvajanju s specialitetami z žara kakor v gril restavracijah v Argentini. Avtohtono meso je sveže dobavljeno in pripravljeno na pravem argentinskem žaru, v katerem tli žerjavica tropskega lesa dreves algerobo, quebracho blanco in bukve. Nudimo vam samo najboljše meso pašne vzreje in kontrolirane kakovosti goveda Black Angus. Argentinska govedina najvišje kakovosti prihaja k nam iz uglednih govejih farm v Argentini, imenovanih “ESTANCIAS”.
Osebje, opravljeno v tradicionalno argentinsko nošo, vam pričara povsem pristen ambient. Vrhunski kuharji za vas pripravijo jedi po tradicionalnih argentinskih receptih na tipičnih žarih, posebej pripeljanih iz Argentine, v katerih tli trd tropski argentinski les dreves algarrobo in quebracho blanco, ki daje hrani prav poseben, edinstven okus. Življenjski prostor argentinskega goveda so pampe, neskončne prerije, polne rodovitnih žitnih polj in bujno zelenih travnikov, kjer se prosto pasejo črede govedi in konj. Zanje skrbijo gavči, legendarni divji jezdeci, ki slovijo kot najboljši strokovnjaki za vzrejo govedi.

item.title: Stadion Stožice
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Šport Ljubljana je ljubljanski zavod za upravljanje s športnimi objekti in površinami, ki so v lasti MOL. Dejavnost Šport Ljubljana je izredno široka, saj pod okriljem zavoda potekajo športne prireditve svetovnega in evropskega pomena, državna tekmovanja, vadba in treningi vrhunskih ekip športnih klubov in društev, ki domujejo na naših objektih. Na voljo so tudi različni tečaji in rekreativni programi vseh vrst. Poslanstvo zavoda je omogočiti kar najboljše možnosti in pogoje za vrhunski in rekreativni šport v Ljubljani.

item.title: City Museum
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
The institution Museum and Galleries of Ljubljana was established in 2009 and comprises the City Museum of Ljubljana, the Jakopič Gallery, the Vžigalica Gallery, the City Art Gallery of Ljubljana, the Bežigrad Gallery 1, the Bežigrad Gallery 2, Galerija 001 and the Tobacco Museum situated in the Tobačna 001 Cultural Centre as well as Plečnik House in Trnovo.
TIMELINE 1935 The Municipality of Ljubljana purchased Auersperg Palace to house the newly established City Museum of Ljubljana; its first collection was put on in one part of the building in 1937. In the following decades, the Museum shared the building with several other institutions. 1954 The City Art Gallery of Ljubljana was set up. 1976 The Bežigrad Gallery with premises at 31 Dunajska street was established. Since 1996, it has been operating as part of the City Art Gallery of Ljubljana. 2002 In 2002, the Bežigrad Gallery 1 saw the addition of new gallery premises – the Bežigrad Gallery 2 at 3 Vodovodna street. 2000 to 2004 In this period, Auersperg Palace which is home to the City Museum of Ljubljana was thoroughly renovated. 2009 A new institution was created, thereby bringing the City Museum of Ljubljana and the City Art Gallery of Ljubljana together, including all related locations. 2010 The Tobačna 001 Cultural Centre, situated in the Tobačna City and incorporating both museal and gallery premises, joined the institution. Plečnik house has been managed by the Museum and Galleries of Ljubljana. Plans for the future include implementation of a conservation-restoration project aiming at preserving Plečnik's original arrangement. Apart from that, new museal contents will be added in that part of the house holding less significance in preservation terms. 2011 In March, Galerija 001 (with an exhibition of the Belgian artist Jan Fabre) and the Tobacco Museum were officially opened. They are both located in the Tobačna 001 Cultural Centre. 2015 The renovation of the Plečnik House is successfully completed.

The Science Museum is the most visited science and technology museum in Europe. There are over 15,000 objects on display, including world-famous objects such as the Apollo 10 command capsule and Stephenson’s Rocket.
Our interactive galleries bring to life first scientific principles and contemporary science debates. Plus, you can experience what it’s like to fly with the Red Arrows or blast off into space on an Apollo space mission in our stunning 3D and 4D simulators or watch a film on a screen taller than four double-decker buses in the IMAX 3D Cinema.

item.title: Hotel Nox
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Located in the Šentvid area of Ljubljana, Hotel Nox offers air-conditioned rooms with large windows and city views. Free Wi-Fi and free private parking are provided. All rooms are modernly decorated and each room has a different design. Room amenities include a flat-screen cable TV, a minibar and a laptop safe. Each bathroom comprises a hairdryer and either a bathtub or a shower. The Nox Hotel offers a breakfast buffet on site, and the nearest restaurant is just across the street. A supermarket can be found at a distance of 50 m. The hotel offers a car rental service and a shuttle service at a surcharge. Guests are welcome to visit the on-site wine cellar which features an extensive wine list. A golf court and several tennis courts are 2 km away. Just in front of the hotel guests can find a public bus stop with lines to the centre of Ljubljana, 6 km away, where the Main Bus and Train Station is located. Krvavec ski slopes and Ljubljana Airport can be found in a 20 km radius.

This property is also rated for the best value in Ljubljana! Guests are getting more for their money when compared to other properties in this city.

We speak your language!

item.title: Radisson Blu Plaza Hotel Ljubljana
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Built in 2012, Radisson Blu Plaza Hotel Ljubljana is located in Ljubljana and offers an à-la-carte restaurant, conference rooms and a gym. It features modern-style accommodation with free WiFi. Guests are offered 4 hours of daily access to the swimming pool at the Atlantis Water Park, set 200 m from the hotel. All accommodation units are decorated in beige tones, and provide modern amenities such as LED satellite TVs and iPod docking stations. Each room features a working area, an orthopaedic bed, a minibar and coffee making facilities. In the picturesque centre of Ljubljana guests can enjoy numerous sights, bars and restaurants offering local cuisine. A bus stop with lines to Ljubljana's centre is in front of the hotel and can be reached with a 7-minute drive. The hotel also provides a taxi service upon request and at a surcharge. Radisson Blu Plaza Hotel Ljubljana is part of the BTC City, the business, commercial and entertainment centre of Ljubljana, which includes the Atlantis Water Park, bowling alleys, indoor carting and tennis courts. There is also a multiplex film theatre, a theatre and more than 400 various shops. A bus stop is 50 m away. The centre of Ljubljana is at a distance of 3 km. Ljubljana International Airport is 25 km from the Ljubljana Plaza Hotel with shuttle service available at a surcharge.

This property is also rated for the best value in Ljubljana! Guests are getting more for their money when compared to other properties in this city.

item.title: Cineplexx
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Podjetje za distribucijo filmov Constantin Film Holding GmbH je bilo ustanovljeno leta 1951 v Avstriji. Druga temeljna veja podjetja na področju kinematografskih dejavnosti je bila ustanovljena proti koncu 60. let prejšnjega stoletja. V tem segmentu je delovalo 25 tradicionalnih kinematografov in kinematografskih centrov, vse do začetka 90-ih, ko je podjetje doživelo strukturno spremembo. Leta 1993 je bila ustanovljena hčerinska družba Constantin Film Holdinga z imenom Cineplexx Cine Operations Gmbh (d.o.o.). Podjetje se je razvijalo v obdobju, ko so mnogi tradicionalni kinematografi v Avstriji postopoma izginjali, kinematografski multipleksi pa so osvajali tržišče. Podjetje Constantin Film je kot odgovor na ta trend izginjanja tradicionalnih kinematografov reagiralo tako, da je ustanovilo skupino 20 kinematografov in 157 kinematografskih platen v Avstriji. Poleg tega je obstalo še nekaj tradicionalnih kinematografov, ki so skupaj imeli do 16 dvoran. Leta 2009 se je podjetje Cineplexx International GmbH začelo širiti v Avstriji sosednje države, prvo kinodvorano izven Avstrije pa je odprlo v Bolzanu na severnem Tirolskem. Cineplexx je prevzel tudi kinodvorano v centru Zagreba, s čimer je položil temeljni kamen za širitev na Hrvaškem. V letih 2011 in 2012 so sledila odprtja Cineplexx kinematografov na Hrvaškem, v Srbiji, Črni gori in Makedoniji. Sledila je širitev podjetja oktobra 2012 , ko je prevzelo 5 multipleksov v Sloveniji: v Celju, Mariboru, Novem mestu, Kranju in Kopru, letu 2013 pa se je pridružila še Murska Sobota s šestim kinematografom Cineplexx v Sloveniji. Najnovejša širitev se je zgodila decembra 2013, ko se je prvi kinematograf Cineplexx odprl v Albanski prestolnici Tirani. Trenutno je tako kar 114 filmskih platen, aktivnih izven Avstrije. S kar 38 multipleksi in 6 tradicionalnimi lokacijami v Avstriji, na Hrvaškem, v Srbiji, Sloveniji, Črni gori, Makedoniji, Albaniji in Italiji je Cineplexx močno zastopan na tržišču in nudi kar okoli 64.000 sedežnih mest v 288 dvoranah. Leta 2012 je delovna sila podjetja štela kar 1100 zaposlenih, skupni prihodki od prodaje so znašali 115 milijonov evrov, število Cineplexxovih obiskovalcev pa je doseglo 10,5 milijonov.

item.title: Grand Hotel Union
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Located just steps away from the central Prešern Square and Tromostovje in Ljubljana, Grand Hotel Union offers accommodation in a historical Art Nouveau building. Free WiFi access is provided in all areas. All spacious and tastefully decorated air-conditioned rooms come with a flat-screen cable TV, a minibar and a safe, while private bathrooms feature a bathtub, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Slippers and bathrobes are provided for your comfort. All guests are welcome to enjoy the complimentary buffet breakfast. Grand Hotel Union is famous for its' Grand Union Café where guests can relax with a cup of coffee or tea accompanied by a varied offer of cakes and pastries in a historic setting. Restaurant and bar Atelje combines international and Slovene cuisine in an intimate and welcoming setting, while the Union Garden Restaurant provides a unique dining experience in the private garden of Grand Hotel Union. The hotel also features a wine library with a selection of Slovene wines and a casual lobby bar. The wellness centre is on the top level of Grand Hotel Union Business and features a swimming pool and saunas that can all be used free of charge. The hotel also has a fitness centre on the mezzanine floor, and a ground floor shopping gallery with a fashion boutique, a jewellery shop, a souvenir shop, a barber and a hairstylist. The congress centre features 21 fully equipped multifunctional halls that cater to all types of events. Ljubljana Old Town can be reached in 180 metres, while the Ljubljanica River Promenade is just 100 m away. Ljubljana Castle is 1 km away, while the Ljubljana Cathedral is at a distance of 500 m. The Main Bus and Railway Station are 700 m away. Ljubljana Airport can be reached in 25 km. Paid covered parking is provided on site.

This is our guests' favourite part of Ljubljana, according to independent reviews.

This property also has one of the best-rated locations in Ljubljana! Guests are happier about it compared to other properties in the area.

item.title: Hiša eksperimentov
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The House of Experiments is for everyone! Science, learning, art and humour all intertwine in the House of Experiments into a whole. This awakens the visitors' curiosity and brings them closer to the natural laws and phenomena from everyday life in a simple and interesting way. During individual researching and carrying out experiments, every visitor learns the truth with "their own skin", the most effective kind of school. A chinese proverb says: »I heard and I forgot. I saw and I rememberd. I did it and I know.« This last is what happens in the House. We would like to create a society of curious and open people who are not afraid to admit and ask what they do not know, and learn about it. The knowledge of individuals becomes richer with personal experience obtained through experimenting, and society becomes richer through the free exchange of ideas among individuals. HE helps build personal experience and open up the flow of information.

item.title: Picerija Etna
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Leta 1991 se v Podutiku odpre picerija Etna, ki se pohvali s svojimi odličnimi picami iz električne peči. Kasneje pice obogati aroma krušne peči in pica postane »pica kraljica 2001« kot ena izmed petih najboljših picerij na slovenskem.
Skozi leta se piceriji pridruži kuhinja in novi ambientalni prostori z raznovrstnim designom. Gurmanske trenutke lahko doživljate v intimnem kotičku, ki ga nudijo separeji ali v domačnosti in sproščenosti celotne restavracije.
Kuhinja ponuja klasične zrezke in steake, pestro ponudbo pašt in morskih dobrot. Gostje najraje naročijo lignje, rostbif, lazanjo, pašto carbonaro in bolognese ter vedno svežo ponudbo tedenskih rib. Morskih gurmanov vsekakor ne manjka in lahko bi se preimenovali v ribjo restavracijo. Ob klasičnih picah sta najbolj prodajani še kmečka in morska pica.

item.title: Strle svetila & design
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Strle svetila smo čisto konkretni ljudje. Z nekaterimi hodimo skupaj že dvajset let. Za nami sta dobri dve desetletji dela in toliko uspešnih projektov, da jih še sami ne znamo več prešteti. Ostali so spomini na lepe projekte in zadovoljne stranke, ki so s časom prerasle v prijatelje, ostale so izkušnje in znanje, na katere smo resnično lahko ponosni. Znanje in srčnost sta tisto, kar vložimo v vsak nov projekt. Eno brez drugega ne gre. Veseli smo vsakega, ki pride k nam po nasvet, po znanje ali idejo. Iščemo racionalne rešitve, ki lovijo ravnotežje med čutnim doživljanjem svetlobe, uporabnostjo objektov in vzdržljivostjo materialov. Luč je živa. Na spletnih straneh vam predstavljamo del naše ponudbe, nekakšen izbor. Nanj so se uvrstila najboljša podjetja, ki so se skozi leta sodelovanja izkazala za kvalitetne partnerje, s katerimi smo zgradili dober poslovni odnos in ki naše stranke navdušujejo s svojimi svetili. Sodelujemo tudi z odličnimi arhitekti, ki so nam pogosto v veliko pomoč. Nekatere skupne projekte boste našli med referenčnimi projekti. Trgovina JZS koncept na Igriški ulici 3 v Ljubljani, že nekaj časa deluje kot ambasada za različna podjetja, saj ta skozi naše izložbene prostore prinašajo v Slovenijo izdelke, ki bi jih sicer lahko občudovali le na fotografijah ali na spletu. JZS koncept, je posvečen predvsem delu z individualnimi strankami in z dolgoletnimi izkušnjami na področju oblikovanja nudi svetovanje in projektiranje rešitev za notranje in zunanje prostore. Skrbi za redno strokovno sodelovanje z različnimi mediji, organizira predstavitve novih svetil in podjetij ter sodeluje s študenti različnih študijev v okviru delavnic in krajših predavanj.

item.title: FLAT
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Where it all began In search of a business opportunity, the three of us - Rebecca Arluck, Aleš Bosančič and Oren Arluck noticed that in Ljubljana, our native city, there was a significant public demand for beautiful design and hardly any businesses providing this sort of goods. In 2007 we decided to open such a shop with a vision to create something that had not existed in our city before – a concept shop with truly special, unique goods from all over the world. Our founding ideal was the same as it is today: to hunt out the most original items from the best creative businesses, and bring them together in one place, making it easy for people to browse and buy. How we've grown We started out in 2007 selling goods from as little as three Italian brands, but with the years our clientele grew more and more and so did the business. Today we sell products from more than forty different designer brands from all over the world. Along with our retail shop in Ljubljana, our work in the field of corporate gift sales has been growing too. Over the years we have provided corporate gifts for small, medium and large companies from across Slovenia. In the last years we have taken on a new challenge and started working as agents and distributors for some important designer brands on the Slovenian and Italian markets. However, our team still consists of three employees and three to four part time assistants, so we remain a very small business. Where we want to be Is it wrong to say ‘everywhere’? Becoming one of Slovenia’s most exciting and fastest-growing retail businesses is just the start of a very exciting journey. With the launch of this webshop we want to make it easy for you to be original – wherever you live, and whatever you’re into. So that means we’ll always be on the lookout for new ideas, up-and-coming designers who are just starting their careers and innovative ways of making something unique, personal and beautiful. And we’ll always make it easy.

item.title: Maros
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Podjetje Maros d.o.o., Šmartinska cesta 53, Ljubljana, je na slovenskem tržišču prisotno že od leta 1990. Na prodajnih mestih v Ljubljani, Celju in Slovenski vasi pri Brežicah  svojim kupcem nudimo vrhunsko evropsko pohištvo srednjega in višjega cenovnega razreda. V toplem in elegantnem ambientu salonov so na celotnem prostoru razstavljene sedežne garniture, naslanjači, kuhinje z belo tehniko ter jedilnice, oprema za dnevni prostor in spalnice, vrtno pohištvo, dodatki za dom od vazic do svetil in preprog, celo naprave za vadbo. Nenazadnje, v salonih kupec najde vse kar potrebujete za opremo doma, od klasičnih do modernih dizajnov. Vodila pri načrtovanju salonov so bila oblikovati predstavitev celotne ponudbe opreme za dom na način, da za kupca sprehod po salonu predstavlja posebno doživetje, popotovanje skozi različne svetove, kjer spoznava odličnost posameznih kosov in kolekcij ter se osredotoči na tisto, kar išče in kar pristaja njegovemu slogu. Izbira pohištva tako ni prepuščena naključju ali zgolj listanju po katalogu, ampak temelji na doživetju kupca v salonu. S strokovno pomočjo naših prodajalcev in arhitektov nudimo najboljše rešitve po meri posameznika. Zastopamo številne svetovno znane blagovne znamke: ekskluzivno za Slovenijo zastopamo NATUZZI, ponudba pa obsega še CALLIGARIS, NOVAMOBILI, TONIN CASA, ELITE, RECORD CUCINE, QUADRIFOGLIO, DOMA-KO, PIETRA KAIKOS, MAEL, DONAR, HERMAN MILLER, ALPLES, CASA DESIGN, AKANTO, ESSEBI, ILES IDRIJA, ITALSOFA  in mnoge druge.
Našo ponudbo gradijo
  • visoko kvalitetno pohištvo;
  • brezplačne strokovne izmere in obisk arhitekta na domu;
  • strokovno svetovanje ob nakupu na osnovi dolgoletnih izkušenj;
  • pravočasno dostavo in brezhibno montažo;

item.title: Bazilika Bistro
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Bazilika se je rodila iz ljubezni do kuhanja, hrane in druženja. Naša osnovna zgodba je družinska in izhaja iz želje biti preprost in hkrati malo drugačen. Pri tem pa si želimo ustvariti zgodbo, ki bo trajala in pustila pečat.
Pri nas ne kompliciramo, delamo s srcem in po navdihu. Vsakič znova se zavemo, da za nas skoraj ni večjega zadovoljstva, kot je pred vas postaviti krožnik domače župce.
Verjamemo, da je vse kar pride iz naše kuhinje zdravo, to pa zato, ker je pripravljeno vedno sveže in iz najboljših sestavin. Zelenjavo naročamo vsak dan sproti, pogosto izbiramo ekološko in lokalno ter, kar se da sezonsko.
V naši shrambi je majhen zamrzovalnik, ki hrani francoske rogljičke in občasno grah, skoraj vse ostalo uporabljamo sveže. Prisegamo na zelišča in olivno olje.

item.title: Le Petit cafe
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Before a morning walk into the old part of Ljubljana, you can stop in a cosy corner for the famous Le Petit white coffee and fresh orange juice. Elegant café, a romantic garden, freshly baked croissants and chansons will conjure up a real french atmosphere.
Among the breakfasts you will find classics of French mornings: Croque Madame & Croque Monsieur, and our culinary creations will impress you in the intimate ambiance of the Le Petit restaurant. Pleasant staff enrich afternoon chatting with friends along a glass of carefully selected wine, advise you and please your wishes.

item.title: Casa Wine & Tapas
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: V lokalu Casa Wine & Tapas v poslovni stavbi Diamant smo pred kratkim razširili svojo ponudbo - od 29. avgusta dalje strežemo kosila vsak delavnik med 11. in 15. uro. Od zdaj naprej vas bo tako od ponedeljka do petka v času kosila v Casi čakala vsakič druga juhica, vedno pa boste lahko izbirali med dvema mesnima, eno vegetarijansko in eno solatno jedjo. Casa je kraj, kamor se lahko odpravite v prav vsakem delu dneva. Že zjutraj lahko pričnete svoj dan z izvrstnim zajtrkom in skodelico vroče kave ali čaja. Dopoldne se lahko okrepčate z različnimi sendviči in toasti. Ljubitelji vina boste prav tako prišli na svoj račun, saj boste lahko ob kosilu izbirali med široko ponudbo vrhunskih vin, tako slovenskih kot tujih pridelovalcev. Kozarec vina si le privoščite tudi zvečer, za »zraven« pa vam v Casi ponujajo različne španske tapase in narezke. V sredini tedna nikar ne pozabite na plesne čevlje, saj so vsako sredo plesni salsa večeri. Ob četrtkih in petkih vas bo pa DJ Zoki popeljal v ritme jugoslovanskega popa in pop glasbe iz 80. in 90. let. Casa Wine & Tapas je svoja vrata odprla v začetku junija. Od takrat je zaradi svojega prijetnega ambienta, kvalitetne ponudbe in prijaznega osebja postala priljubljena točka v ljubljanskem BTC-ju. Vlado Petek, solastnik, je o Casi povedal: »Casa je novo prijetno mesto za druženje v BTC-ju. Ekipa Case je strokovno usposobljena, da zadovolji tudi naše najbolj zahtevne goste, kar se je pokazalo v kratkem času našega delovanja. Imamo odlično kavo, odlična kosila in ugodne cene, kar nam vsakodnevno pritrjujejo naši stalni in občasni gostje.

item.title: Sax Pub
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is what happens when an unruly youth inherits his great aunt’s country cottage. This now legendary, graffiti-spattered nightspot wouldn’t last a week in New Orleans, but in Ljubljana there’s nothing of its kind to beat it. A fairly small bar features photographs of jazz greats on the walls and a clientele of people who appreciate what Charles Mingus once referred to as black classical music. Most of the time the music is pre-recorded, but they do have the occasional live band in from time to time.
(Inyourpocket.com Essential City Guides)
In Trnovo and decorated with colorful murals and graffiti inside and out, Sax has live jazz at 21.30 on Thursday
(lonelyplanet.com)
Sax pub is located on Eipprova Street. It was the first pub in the street. After that, a lot of other cafes and restaurants opened their doors but despite others you can’t really miss Sax pub. It’s a small house covered with graffiti.You could call it the second jazz club in Ljubljana as it has a stage smaller than a normal toilet. It’s well known for great atmosphere, especially during the summer, when they have concerts on a stage near Gradascica River, which was made by Slovenian architect Joze Plecnik. The place is perfect for a break from the center if you don’t have enough time to go somewhere further away. You will find Eipprova Street south of the center in the city part called Trnovo. It is also possible to walk there from Preseren’s square, if you just walk along Ljubljanica River.
(spottedbylocals.com)

item.title: Železniški muzej
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Železniški muzej je začel nastajati v šestdesetih letih in se je v nekdanji kurilnici na Parmovi 35 postopoma razvil v manjši, a izoblikovan in celovit muzej. V osrednjem objektu, rotundi, je na ogled del zbirke parnih lokomotiv in drugih muzejskih vozil. Stalna razstava drugih ključnih strok, potrebnih, da železnica lahko deluje, je v bližnjem pomožnem objektu rotunde.
Tu je mogoče v prvem prostoru podoživeti ozračje prometnega urada manjše železniške postaje iz zadnjih let avstro-ogrske monarhije, ki je opremljen z vsemi potrebščinami za izvajanje prometa in prodajo vozovnic.
V drugem prostoru je devet tipov tirnih polj iz različnih obdobij in železniških uprav, kakor so se pač menjavali oblastniki pri nas. Mala tirna vozila, drezine, ki stojijo na njih, so nekoč služila nadzornikom proge in vzdrževalcem. O nekdanjem težavnem vzdrževanju pričajo ročna orodja in pripomočki. Razvoj železniškega omrežja na Slovenskem je predstavljen s sedmimi zemljevidi iz različnih časovnih obdobij, ob katerih kot priče iz preteklosti stojijo stari železniški mejniki.
Eden od muzejskih prostorov je namenjen temeljnim napravam za prenos sporočil, kot so telegrafi, telefoni in teleprinterji, pa tudi aparatom višje ravni, namreč kratkovalovnim in UKV radijskim postajam, napravam za registriranje telefonskih pogovorov, postajnemu ozvočenju, pa tudi sistemu železniških ur.
Poseben prostor je namenjen železniški uniformi, "častnemu oblačilu", kakor se je oblikovala skozi čas. Tu so zbrani tudi nekateri delovni pripomočki železničarja, med katerimi so še posebej simpatične železniške ročne svetilke.
S področja signalnovarnostnih naprav je na ogled reprezentativna zbirka elektromehanskih in elektrodinamičnih bločnih naprav in drugih aparatov – tako izdelkov iz najstarejše kot tudi iz polpretekle dobe. Zastopane so najbolj razširjene naprave, a tudi posebnosti in unikati.
Majhna likovna galerija seznanja obiskovalce z umetnostjo, posvečeno železnici.

item.title: City Hotel Ljubljana
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: City Hotel is located in the very heart of Ljubljana and is an excellent choice for both business guests and tourists to discover the charms of Ljubljana and Slovenia. It has a wonderful view of Ljubljana Castle and the city cathedral, and an ideal location just a stone’s throw from the historic old town. This pleasant hotel among the vibrant city inns, shops, and attractive historical buildings offers local Slovenian and international cuisine as well as a state-of-the-art congress center. The Jože Pučnik international airport is only 25 km from the hotel, and the main railway and bus station is only 400 m away. The hotel is easy to access from all of the city’s major roads; once in the city, you simply follow the blue hotel signs. Ljubljana’s City Hotel is the successor to the venerable Štrukelj Hotel, which opened in 1907. The current hotel excels in its friendly staff, the warmth of its rooms, and a broad range of services found at an excellent location in the very city center. City Hotel has 201 rooms, three luxury suites, an underground garage, a conference center with four meeting rooms, a library, a terrace, an Internet corner, a restaurant, and a bar. City Hotel’s complete makeover concluded with its opening in September 2007. The “basic” and “standard” rooms were renovated, and the “superior” rooms were moved to a completely new part of the hotel. All of the rooms use a card-locking system and all of them have free Internet access.

item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Ljudem bi radi pokazali lepoto vina in mnogim želimo svetovati pri nakupu vina. Radi bi ponudil informacije prav vsem, kadarkoli in kjerkoli na svetu.
Spletna trgovina eVino ponuja priznane slovenske in tuje vinogradnike, ki bodo z svojimi vini poskušali zadovoljiti prav vsak okus. Prav tako smo ekskluzivni zastopniki za kozarce Riedel ter še mnogo drugih stvari.

item.title: Europcar
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Želite prihraniti pri stroških službene poti? Lastna vozila predstavljajo podjetju vsakodnevni strošek, najeta vozila pa le takrat ko jih zares potrebujete. Najem vozila za kratkoročne ali dolgoročne potrebe je vsekakor prava rešitev. Zakaj? Europcar kratkoročni in prilagodljivi mesečni najemi vključujejo prav vse stroške vozila: zavarovanje vozila, vzdrževanje, registracijo, zimske pnevmatike...
  1. Vozilo najamete za tako dolgo, kot ga dejansko potrebujete.
  2. Brez zapletenih leasing pogodb in kreditiranja vozila.
  3. Najem lahko podaljšate za poljubno število mesecev (od 1 do 12 mesecev).
  4. Najem zaključite, ko vam to najbolj ustreza in to z 0 EUR  odpovedi
  5. Ob morebitni okvari vozila vam zagotavljamo 24 urno asistenco ali nadomestno vozilo
Prikaz stroškov, ko za potrebe službenih poti zaposleni uporabljajo lastno vozilo

item.title: Klobasarna
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Znanje izdelovanja kranjskih klobas izvira iz stoletne tradicije kolin, največjega posvetnega praznika naših prednikov. Poimenovanje klobase z opredelitvijo »kranjska« izvira iz zgodnjega 19. stoletja, iz časov Avstroogrske monarhije. Z njim se je označilo geografsko poreklo te posebne mesene klobase. Ime izdelka »kranjska klobasa« vsebuje torej popolnoma določeno geografsko opredelitev, ki jo predstavlja na slovenskem narodnostnem ozemlju od 15. stoletja osrednja zgodovinska dežela, ki je bila od vseh ostalih dežel edina povsem slovenska. Zato je bil izraz Kranjec tudi drugo ime za Slovenca. Kot posebna dežela v okviru Avstroogrske monarhije je Kranjska prenehala obstajati leta 1918, njena »dedinja« pa je današnja republika Slovenija.

Najstarejši recept za kranjsko klobaso je zapisala med potovanjem po nekdanjem Kranjskem znamenita kuharica Katharina Prato oz. Pratobevera in ga objavila v delu »Süddeutsche Küche«, leta 1896 (prva izdaja 1858). V slovenskem jeziku je bil recept prvič v celoti zapisan v šesti izdaji »Slovenske kuharice« Felicite Kalinšek l.1912.

item.title: Hotel Cubo
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Hotel Cubo is located in the centre of Ljubljana. It offers modern, air-conditioned rooms with free access to Wi-Fi and a flat-screen cable TV and a fine restaurant. Guests can enjoy delicate international cuisine in the restaurant. A large selection of drinks is offered at the bar. The luxuriously furnished rooms have a seating area, a work desk and a transparent bathroom. Bathrobes, slippers and toiletries are provided. Guests can enjoy breakfast in the restaurant or in the privacy of their own room. This 4-star hotel has a 24-hour front desk and organizes laundry service and airport shuttles. Hotel Cubo is 1.6 km away from Ljubljana Train and Bus Station.

This is our guests' favourite part of Ljubljana, according to independent reviews.

This property also has one of the best-rated locations in Ljubljana! Guests are happier about it compared to other properties in the area.

This property is also rated for the best value in Ljubljana! Guests are getting more for their money when compared to other properties in this city.

We speak your language!

item.title: Verace
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The most widely recognized pizza with tomatoes, mozzarella and basil was not created until the second half of the 19th century, when it was immortalised by queen Margherita of Savoy. During her majesty’s visit to Naples she craved to taste a dish she encountered at her every footstep, but never made its way to the royal table. There is no coincidence the celebrated pizza bears all colours found in the flag of Italy.

item.title: Moderna galerija
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Moderna galerija (Museum of Modern and Contemporary Art) is the Slovene national institution for modern and contemporary art. As a museum of Slovene modern art it explores and presents the 20th-century Slovene art tradition, while as a museum of contemporary art and exhibition venue it presents new art practices and their context.
It is also a documentary, study, research and education centre, a place for discussions and reflection and for presenting art to a wider audience.

item.title: Element-are
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: 1.      Znanje in storitve Vsako gospodinjstvo si zasluži kvaliteten bivalni prostor. Dvig bivanjske kulture pripomore k boljšemu počutju, produktivnosti in omogoča da se v svojem domu po napornem dnevu sprostimo in spočijemo. Poleg pestre ponudbe pohištvenih elementov zato nudimo tudi storitev oblikovanja interierja. Dobra funkcionalna zasnova omogoča fleksibilen ambient, ki ga uporabnik lahko personalizira. Naročnik projekta poleg rešitve prostora pridobi dodatne ugodnosti ob naročilu tipskega pohištva in možnost sodelovanja z našimi preverjenimi mizarji. 2. Komuniciramo, razmislimo in rešimo Naši kupci ne pričakujejo le storitev, naši kupci pričakujejo človeka. Svetujemo vam izkušeni oblikovalci interierja in arhitekti, v skladu z vašimi željami in pričakovanji pripravimo funkcionalno, oblikovno in estetsko najboljše rešitve za vaš prostor. Nudimo vam gotovost izbire, varnost odločitve in kakovost storitve. 3. Oblikujemo in izrišemo Izbrane koncepte povežemo v celoto ter jim vdihnemo prostorsko predstavo. Za vas izdelamo tlorise, poglede iz različnih zornih kotov in 3-D vizualizacije. 4. Obiščemo na domu, pregledamo in izmerimo Skupaj z vami načrtujemo umestitev pohištva v vaš prostor. Natančno preverimo vse dimenzije, preučimo značilnosti vašega bivalnega okolja in glede na dejansko stanje predlagamo morebitne spremembe.

item.title: Furnitura
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Podjetje Furnitura, spletna trgovina d.o.o. je zavezano odličnosti na področju spletnega nakupovanja. Sledimo potrebam sodobnih kupcev in stremimo k najboljši, uporabniku prijazni nakupovalni izkušnji.
Podjetje je bilo ustanovljeno aprila 2010 z namenom odpreti spletno trgovino s pohištvom, ki bi slovenskim kupcem končno lahko ponudila današnjemu času primeren način nakupovanja pohištva in opremljanja doma. Julija 2010 odprti spletni salon SalonPohistva.si je kmalu postal vodilna slovenska spletna trgovina s pohištvom in izdelki za dom.
SalonPohistva.si kupcem ponuja široko paleto kvalitetnih izdelkov uglednih domačih in tujih blagovnih znamk po ugodnih cenah. Stalno si prizadevamo, da bi strankam, tako fizičnim kot pravnim osebam, omogočili najboljšo možno nakupovalno izkušnjo in celovito ponudbo. Našo ponudbo stalno dopolnjujemo in širimo z mislijo na ideal spletnega mesta, ki bi omogočilo celovito opremo vsakega doma.
Vzpostavljeno imamo široko razvejano mrežo priznanih domačih in tujih dobaviteljev, kot so Colombini, IMAB, Sintesi, Lineaflex, SITAP, Eglo, Hitex, Odeja in Klun Ambienti. V letu 2012 smo začeli z širitvijo poslovanja na druge trge EU, ki ga bomo v letu 2013 še razširili.

item.title: Congress Square
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The square was built in 1821 at the site of the ruins of a medieval Capuchin monastery, which had been abolished during the reign of Habsburg Emperor Joseph II. The square was used for ceremonial purposes during the Congress of Ljubljana, after which it was named. After the congress, a park was laid out in the center of the square, which soon acquired the name Star Park (Slovene: Park Zvezda, German: Sternallee) due to its layout. During the communist period it was renamed Revolution Square (Slovene: Trg revolucije) and a few years later Liberation Square (Slovene: Trg osvoboditve), but the local population continued to use the old name. In 1990, it regained its original name. The square has had a highly symbolic role in modern Slovenian history. On October 29, 1918, independence from Austrian-Hungarian rule and the establishment of the State of Slovenes, Croats and Serbs was proclaimed during a mass demonstration on the square. In May 1945, the Yugoslav Communist leader Josip Broz Tito first visited Slovenia after World War II and held a speech on the balcony of the University of Ljubljana, which faces the square. On June 22, 1988, the first free mass demonstration was held on the square demanding the release of four Slovene journalists imprisoned by the Yugoslav army. The demonstration marked the beginning of the Slovenian spring which culminated in the declaration of Slovenia's independence on June 25, 1991. Independence was first demanded in the May Declaration, written by the Slovenian democratic opposition and signed by numerous civil society movements; the declaration was first publicly read by the poet Tone Pavček in a demonstration on Congress Square on May 8, 1989. In 1999 Bill Clinton became the first U.S. president to visit Slovenia. On June 21, he publicly addressed the crowd gathered on Congress Square, quoting the opening verses of the Slovenian national anthem.

item.title: Nova KBM
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Nova Kreditna banka Maribor je ena vodilnih slovenskih finančnih institucij in je s skoraj 400.000 komitenti druga največja banka v državi. Povezana s Poštno banko Slovenije komitentom nudi celovit in široko dostopen bančno-finančni servis v skupno 614 poslovalnicah po vsej Sloveniji.
Klasične bančne storitve dopolnjujemo s ponudbo družb finančne skupine NKBM, ki vključuje zavarovalništvo, vzajemne sklade in storitve borznega posredništva. Naše storitve odlikujejo učinkovitost, varnost, zanesljivost in osebni pristop pri reševanju finančnih izzivov posameznika.

item.title: Ziferblat Ljubljana
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Ziferblat is a place where everyone can feel at home. Here you are free to be yourself; you can work, do some art, read a book, play piano, get acquainted with good people, attend events, drink as much tea or coffee as you want — in other words, do whatever you like as long as you respect the space and the other people in it.
Ziferblat’s doors are open to everyone. Each Ziferblat guest becomes a sort of micro-tenant of the space, responsible for it and able to influence its life.
You will be welcomed by the Ziferblat community and able to work with them to help create, supply and develop this project.
Everything is free inside except the time you spend there; and by paying for the time you’ll be making a donation towards the further development of this social experiment.

item.title: Valvasor
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Opened in July 2008, Valvas’or is a restaurant, located at Stari Trg 7, Ljubljana. It owes its name to the famous Slovene man Janez Vajkard Valvazor, who was born in the house across the street from the restaurant. Hiding behind the typology of his name is a dash of what composes the red thread of the establishment; history, novelty, gold (prestige). The restaurant is designed as a modern, sober space, within an old, arched tavern, accessible from the ground floor. The idea was to create a space where old and new harmoniously unite to create the restaurant’s unique image. To preserve the charm and character of the old space, maintain a feeling of spaciousness, add the necessary elements for the activities currently implemented, design the whole in the spirit of our time, add a metropolitan touch and create a gourmet atmosphere in which to enjoy delicious food – such was the ambition of the authors. The elongated restaurant is built on three levels. The ground floor level with the view of the street is the widest. Here we find the entrance to the restaurant, following which, on the left-hand side, stands a set of tables placed before a brown leather box-element, which serves as the sitting area. To the right-hand side, beneath a pair of gold metal chandeliers, are two round tables suitable for 6 to 8 guests. The tables are situated in front of a golden, perforated metal wall, which breaks at an angle of 90 degrees to continue into the interior of the room, where the ground-and second floor of the restaurant are connected with a flight of stairs. The metal wall continues on the second floor, where, at the kitchen entrance, it breaks again to swathe the sanitary facilities and storage cabinets it conceals. The wall consists of a perforated metal sheet bearing a motif of 16th century Ljubljana, behind which a mirror has been placed to give the room greater depth and to give the wall an impression of lightness. The second floor comprises the kitchen entrance, two console tables with bar stools and additional stairs, which lead to the golden room, the upper floor of the restaurant. Here we encounter a bar, seating in guise of a leather box-element and tables for those who wish to withdraw and be less exposed to the street. The restaurant’s interior is dominated by warm tones. The walls are of a creamy beige colour, the seats are chocolate brown, the floors and tables are in teak and the wall, chandeliers and upper room are golden. The sole black element is a rectangular conduit that uninterruptedly winds throughout the entire establishment and serves lighting and ventilation purposes. In an attempt to highlight the old, pre-existing volume, the authors chose to hide all the lighting in a black technical conduit, with the exception of two gold chandeliers above the round tables and the indirect lighting on the box-element seating, which illuminates and highlights the vaults of the room. The sanitary facilities, which are hidden behind the golden wall, are black, except for the big white sinks and WCs. The restaurant Valvas’or is intended for lovers of good food and the downtown atmosphere, who do not necessarily associate this with all that characterises previous centuries.

Think.Eat.Drink provides guidance, advice and support on many different levels, ranging from food and drink menus, vision, strategies, sustainable design and advice, waste strategies to ethical suppliers and procurement. We have a broad range of experience managing change across a variety of organisations.

item.title: Sarajevo ’84
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Kako se je družinski izlet, več njih, spremenil v željo po tem, da ne bi bilo potrebno narediti nekaj urno pot, da bi se človek počutil kot v Sarajevu vsaj za trenutek.
Pot do čevabdžinice Sarajevo 84 v Ljubljani se je začela z izletom v Sarajevo. Leta nazaj.
Zima, Bjelašnica in notranjost sarajevskih kavarn, barov in klubov je pustila pečat dobrega počutja. Preprosto ni bilo potrebno ničesar drugega, nobene posebne animacije, zgolj Sarajevsko pivo in sposobnost, da se sprostiš, da ujameš energijo Sarajeva in začutiš, kako mesto diha. Počutiš se doma in hočeš ostati. Ne gre se ti nikamor več. Samo od ene postaje Sarajeva proti drugi…

item.title: LIP BLED
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
The LIP BLED Group is the largest exporter among the Slovene wood-processing companies. More than three-quarters of our products are sold on the highly competitive and demanding western and central European markets. Our production processes meet the latest technological standards and we have been successfully operating on the German market for over 50 years. This has helped us develop products which give full weight to the needs of our customers and the environment. In using customer- and environmentally-friendly materials, we support sustainable production, for which we have received the coveted PEFC certificate. The materials we use are regularly tested by renowned Slovene and international institutes. Our successful business operation is also attested by our AA credit rating of excellence. The LIP BLED Group consists of:
  • LIP BLED, d.o.o.: production and sale of interior doors (one of the 20 largest European producers of interior doors);
  • LIP Bohinj, d.o.o.: production and sale of formwork panels used in the construction industry (one of the 4 largest European producers of formwork panels).

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
